### Create Account
POST http://localhost:3000/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "owner": "Francisco"
}

### Deposit (replace ID with the account_id from create response)
POST http://localhost:3000/accounts/REPLACE_WITH_ACCOUNT_ID/deposit
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "amount": 50000
}

### Withdraw (replace ID with the account_id from create response)
POST http://localhost:3000/accounts/REPLACE_WITH_ACCOUNT_ID/withdraw
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "amount": 15000
}

### Deposit invalid amount
POST http://localhost:3000/accounts/REPLACE_WITH_ACCOUNT_ID/deposit
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "amount": -100
}

### Withdraw insufficient funds
POST http://localhost:3000/accounts/REPLACE_WITH_ACCOUNT_ID/withdraw
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "amount": 99999999
}

### Account not found
POST http://localhost:3000/accounts/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/deposit
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "amount": 1000
}
